Good progress! The subscriptions are working. Now for the broadcast:

The error is: `"Param '(root)' doesn't allow key: broadcast"` - This means the `magicbell broadcast create` command also doesn't take a `{"broadcast": {...}}` wrapper; it takes the fields directly at root level (similar to how user save works without the `{"user": {...}}` wrapper).

So the broadcast payload should be:
```json
{
  "title": "Topic Subs CLI - ${ZEALT_RUN_ID}",
  "content": "Broadcast to all subscribers of topic ${TOPIC_KEY}",
  "topic": "${TOPIC_KEY}",
  "recipients": [
    {
      "topic": {
        "subscribers": true
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

